    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You will need to setup a <code>Tomcat</code> Webserver and deploy your web application there.</p>\n\n<p>While deploying the web application you will specify a path to that application (e.G. 'test').</p>\n\n<p>Then you can address your service like: <code>http://myHostname.cx/test/service/MyClass/myRESTMethod?parameter=value</code></p>\n"
